  lower bound.
- Third priority: Chain `01`.
  It is the cleanest surviving positive-family theorem route and helps prevent
  the obstruction story from overclaiming beyond what the carried `F_SL` family
  really earns.
- Keep Chain `04` active despite its lower floor.
  It has the highest counterexample upside because it is the only branch that
  can still kill the firewall idea with a fresh explicit exact construction.

